<h3>Missing Timesheet Entry/Shift Requests</h3>

<p class="mt-2">
  <b>Did you work a shift, and is there no timesheet entry for it?</b> Use
  the "New Missing Timesheet Request" button at the bottom to submit a request.
  You may submit more than one request.
</p>
<p>
  <b>Is a timesheet entry wrong?</b> Do not use the Missing Timesheet Request form,
  instead go back to the <LinkTo @route="me.timesheet-corrections.review">Timesheet Review</LinkTo> page
  and mark the entry as incorrect.
</p>

<Me::TimesheetMissingCommon @person={{person}} @timesheetsMissing={{timesheetsMissing}} @timesheetInfo={{timesheetInfo}} @positions={{positions}} />

<div class="mt-4">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-6 mb-2">
      <LinkTo @route="me.timesheet-corrections.review" class="btn btn-success">{{fa-icon "arrow-left"}} Timesheet Review</LinkTo>
    </div>
    <div class="col-6 text-md-right">
      <LinkTo @route="me.timesheet-corrections.confirm" class="btn btn-success">Final Confirmation {{fa-icon "arrow-right"}}</LinkTo>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
